# 16. TELEGRAM BOT API
# ==============================================================================
# What it's for: Share blog post links to Telegram channels
#
# Steps to obtain:
# 1. Open Telegram app
# 2. Search for @BotFather
# 3. Send /newbot command
# 4. Follow the prompts:
#    - Choose bot name (e.g., "Omni Publisher Bot")
#    - Choose bot username (must end in 'bot', e.g., "omnipublisher_bot")
